gomodel:SYNGO_2402  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Knockdown of DGKZ decreases spine density.\nReduced PA production and spine density in DGKZ KO mice.\nReduced excitatory synaptic transmission in DGKZ KO mice.\nKnockdown of DGKZ affects the maintenance but not formation of dendritic spines.. Experimental description: Materials and methods\nDiOlistic spine labelling and image analysis\nTranscardially perfused 3-week-old mice brain slices were labelled by the ballistic delivery of the lipophilic dye DiI.\n\nNeuron culture and transfection\nCultured neurons prepared from rat hippocampi at E18 were maintained in neurobasal medium supplemented with B27." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6194-9648" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5518-6584" ;
        dc:date           "2018-02-07" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_BP_2402" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10090" .

